              "role": "user",
              "content": "Analyze this video asset:\n\nFilename: {{$json.name}}\nSize: {{$json.size}} bytes\nModified: {{$json.modifiedTime}}\n\nDetermine:\n1. Brand association\n2. Video type (short-form, long-form, raw footage, etc.)\n3. Platform optimization status\n4. Quality and resolution assessment\n5. Repurposing opportunities\n6. Archive vs active status\n\nProvide management recommendations."
            }
