              "role": "user",
              "content": "Process this audio asset:\n\nFilename: {{$json.name}}\nSize: {{$json.size}} bytes\nModified: {{$json.modifiedTime}}\n\nAnalyze:\n1. Audio type (voiceover, music, sound effect, etc.)\n2. Brand relevance\n3. Quality assessment\n4. Usage potential\n5. Optimization needs\n6. Licensing considerations\n\nProvide categorization and recommendations."
            }
