              "role": "user",
              "content": "Analyze the current asset collection and provide optimization recommendations:\n\nTotal Images: {{$('Log Image Assets').all().length}}\nTotal Videos: {{$('Log Video Assets').all().length}}\nTotal Audio: {{$('Log Audio Assets').all().length}}\n\nProvide:\n1. Asset utilization analysis\n2. Gap identification (missing asset types)\n3. Quality improvement recommendations\n4. Cross-brand synergy opportunities\n5. Revenue generation potential\n6. Storage optimization suggestions\n7. Workflow integration improvements\n\nFocus on maximizing content creation efficiency and revenue potential."
            }
          ]
