              "role": "user",
              "content": "With {{$('Filter Image Assets').all().length + $('Filter Video Assets').all().length + $('Filter Audio Assets').all().length}} total assets available, create an automated content generation strategy:\n\n1. Asset combination workflows\n2. Automated remix opportunities\n3. Cross-platform content variations\n4. Batch processing recommendations\n5. Revenue multiplication strategies\n6. Quality control automation\n\nFocus on scaling content production while maintaining quality and brand consistency."
