      "parameters": {
        "channel": "={{$env.DISCORD_CHANNEL_ID}}",
        "text": "📁 **ASSET MANAGEMENT REPORT**\n\n**Asset Inventory:**\n🖼️ Images: {{$('Log Image Assets').all().length}}\n🎬 Videos: {{$('Log Video Assets').all().length}}\n🎵 Audio: {{$('Log Audio Assets').all().length}}\n📊 Total Assets: {{$('Log Image Assets').all().length + $('Log Video Assets').all().length + $('Log Audio Assets').all().length}}\n\n**Strategic Analysis:**\n{{$('Generate Asset Strategy').item.json.choices[0].message.content}}\n\n**Asset Organization:**\n✅ All assets categorized and analyzed\n✅ Brand associations identified\n✅ Usage recommendations provided\n✅ Quality assessments completed\n✅ Cross-brand opportunities mapped\n\n**Next Actions:**\n🎯 Implement optimization recommendations\n🔄 Update content workflows\n💰 Explore revenue opportunities\n📈 Monitor asset utilization\n\n*Asset library is organized and optimized for maximum content creation efficiency!* 🚀"
      },
